00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:39.389
Jutri? Ne, ljubica.

00:04:39.399 --> 00:04:41.310
Troje lahko počneš
na Patriotski dan.

00:04:41.319 --> 00:04:43.430
Prvič, gledaš maraton,
drugič, tečeš maraton

00:04:43.439 --> 00:04:46.509
in tretjič, greš v Fenway
in navijaš za Red Soxe.

00:04:46.519 --> 00:04:48.470
Navijaš za Red Sox.
-Sox.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:51.029
Sox.
-Mmm. Red "Sahx."

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.310
Red "Sahx."
-Red "Sahx."

00:04:53.319 --> 00:04:56.550
Tako, ja. -Mislim, da hočeš le
cel dan ostati z mano v postelji.

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:58.230
Hočeš vedeti, kaj jaz mislim?

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:01.829
Mislim, da je ga. Flanagan
hotela, da imaš obesek,

00:05:01.839 --> 00:05:05.071
ker je vedela, da ga boš
objela, ko ti ga bo dal.

00:05:07.199 --> 00:05:09.910
Zelo si prijazen.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:12.593
Vem. Na zdravje.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:15.637
Na Red Soxe.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:18.870
Ja. "Sahx."

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:23.790
Sox.
- "Sahx."

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:25.278
"Sahx."

